      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\udc4b You have to see this absolute beauty! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one and it\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, it still feels brand new. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person\u2014not a speck out of place! I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely fall in love with it. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728",
