    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior paint retains its original showroom depth, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather seats still possess their factory-fresh scent and matte finish, while the high-resolution displays and all switchgear show zero signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with a complete file of service records included. Every component, from the pristine alloy wheels to the spotless engine bay, reflects a life of pampered ownership. This is a rare find for a discerning collector or enthusiast seeking a vehicle that looks and performs as if it just left the assembly line.",
      "price": 43950.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
